source.name: Percent of Short-Term Rentals Issued by Census Tract
source.description: This data demonstrates the number of short term rental licenses that have been issued in each census tract in Austin. There is a 3 percent cap on the number of short-term rentals permitted. The Licenses Remaining column shows how many licenses are available in that census tract.
